OL,3,CVenice begins charging day-trippers E5
OL,4,Cto enter city
OL,6,FVenice has launched its pilot plan to
OL,7,Fcharge day-trippers five euros to
OL,8,Fenter the city, in an attempt visiting.
OL,10,FThose only spending the day in the
OL,11,Fcity will need to pay if they are
OL,12,Farriving between 8.30am and 4pm.
OL,13,FOutside of those hours people will be
OL,14,Ffree to come and go as they please.
OL,16,FThose tourists also staying within the
OL,17,Fcity are exempt from the charge.
