OL,6,FOnce past the designated entry points,
OL,7,Fofficials will carry out random checks
OL,8,Ffor the code that show the day-tripper
OL,9,Ftax has been paid or that the bearer
OL,10,Fis exempt.
OL,12,FAnybody found to have dodged the fare
OL,13,Ffaces fines of between 50 euros to 300
OL,14,Feuros (#42-#257).
OL,16,F"We need to find a new balance between
OL,17,Fthe tourists and residents,'' the
OL,18,Fcity's top tourism official Simone
OL,19,FVenturini said.
